    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_04-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ…………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa…………",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.266666666666666,
      "endTime": 12.666666690508524,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.866666690508524
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_04-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "最近の莉央\nホントにため息ばっかりだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Lately‚ you’ve\nbeen sighing a lot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.866666690508524,
      "endTime": 16.478503410021464,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_04-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "あの時の私は最低よ\n凄い自己嫌悪……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was the worst back then.\nI’m filled with self-loathing……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.700000023841852,
      "endTime": 21.366666690508517,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.600000023841854
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_04-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "手を上げるのは良くないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You shouldn’t raise your hand to someone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.600000023841854,
      "endTime": 23.591065812110898,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.791065812110897
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_04-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "分かってるわよ\n反省してるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know.\nI'm reflecting on it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.791065812110897,
      "endTime": 26.459342408180238,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――琴乃との一件を莉央は打ち明けた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Rio had confessed about the incident with Kotono.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.95773247877758,
      "endTime": 29.324399145444243,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.9577324787776
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.3243991454442
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "葵にはなんでも話す約束だったからだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was because they promised to tell each other everything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.324399145444243,
      "endTime": 31.70439925988516,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.924399145444244
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_04-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "莉央って、たまに僕より子供だよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio‚ sometimes you’re more childish than me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.924399145444244,
      "endTime": 34.87439924081168,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.07439924081168
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_04-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "容赦のない子ね……\nはぁ～～～～っ………………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re merciless……\nHaa～～～～!………………",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.07439924081168,
      "endTime": 39.707732574145005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.94106590747834
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_04-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "（ほんと、頭にくる……）\n（あの子じゃなくて、未熟過ぎる自分に……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(It really pisses me off……)\n(Not at her‚ but at myself for being so immature……)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.94106590747834,
      "endTime": 46.807732574145014,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.07439924081168
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_04-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "あの子は長瀬麻奈じゃない。妹だよ\nどうして莉央がそこまでムキになるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’s not Mana Nagase. She’s her little sister.\nWhy are you getting so worked up about it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.07439924081168,
      "endTime": 53.70503431161246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.90773257414501
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_04-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "分からないのよ、自分でも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t know‚ myself……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.90773257414501,
      "endTime": 56.24798192183177,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.69188603560131
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_04-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "（葵の言う通りだわ。あの子は長瀬麻奈じゃない）\n（ただの新人アイドル）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Aoi is right. She's not Mana Nagase.)\n(Just a rookie idol.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.69188603560131,
      "endTime": 63.02227152983348,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_04-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "（私達よりずっと格下）\n（なのに、どうしてこんなに心をかき乱されるの……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Far below us.)\n(But why does she shake me up so much……)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.3918860356013,
      "endTime": 69.71950492064158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.19188603560131
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_04-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "僕と莉央は\n長瀬麻奈に勝つためにステージに立つ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio and I‚\nwe stand on stage to beat Mana Nagase.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.19188603560131,
      "endTime": 74.39188613096874,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.82521936893463
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_04-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "LizNoirが\n生前の長瀬麻奈より上だと証明するために",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To prove that LizNoir\nis above Mana Nagase when she was alive.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.82521936893463,
      "endTime": 79.90621712207793,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.08962519522066
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_04-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "それでいいよね？\n彼女は関係ないよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s enough‚ right?\nShe doesn’t matter‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.08962519522066,
      "endTime": 83.70205152387972,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.89652871114237
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_04-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、そうよ\n……ありがとう、葵。もう落ち着いたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ that's right.\n……Thank you‚ Aoi. I’ve calmed down now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.89652871114237,
      "endTime": 89.13231114369852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.32986204447572
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_04-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "いいよ、莉央は疲れてるんだ\n僕と違ってなんに対しても真面目だから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s okay‚ you’re tired.\nUnlike me‚ you're serious about everything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.32986204447572,
      "endTime": 95.99693701090638,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.1965287111424
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_04-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "今日はもう上がりなよ\n家でゆっくり休めばいい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You should go home now.\nJust relax at home.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.1965287111424,
      "endTime": 99.32671007138715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_04-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう\nそうね、今日はこれで帰るわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you.\nYou’re right‚ I’ll head home now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.76319537780918,
      "endTime": 103.94970336578525,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.12986204447593
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
